README

HOW TO INSTALL MIR KERNEL ON DEBIAN / UBUNTU:


apt install cpanminus
apt install make build-essential

cpanm AnyEvent
cpanm EV
cpanm AnyEvent::HTTPD

Thats all

Try to start: 
./scripts/mir



INSTALL nginx:
STEP BY STEP
cd nginx/nginx-1.22.0-src
./configure --prefix=../
make
make install
cd ../
cp nginx.conf conf/nginx.conf
cd ../

STARTING NGINX:
cd nginx/sbin && ./nginx && cd ../../

Try to open in browser:
http://127.0.0.1:3000/

Thats all, may to to code mir

